1080,"file_path":"/z3yu62NzObe7PWJgYbkxOU2QinL.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":2,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/dVrywWj6scjfeaaysDytS4fSO9i.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/1o2VKv03GuwZfL0YyA52ryh4xxx.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/hwBzUKSgxDHrXxGkOPi7boXbGds.jpg","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/aiM43ynPKkfFPGhBQqRUdD62ety.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/nTOmnw7ybBlDQRqUtJMFcLjutD5.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-25T03:51:27.652+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":103,"tagline":"Serve no master","homepage":"http://www.universalstudiosentertainment.com/unleashed/","overview":"Raised as a slave, Danny is used to fighting for his survival. In fact, his \"master,\" Bart, thinks of him as a pet and goes as far as leashing him with a collar so they can make money in fight clubs, where Danny is the main contender. When Bart's crew is in a car accident, Danny escapes and meets a blind, kindhearted piano tuner who takes him in and uses music to free the fighter's long-buried heart."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Unleashed - Entfesselt","runtime":102,"tagline":"Zum Kämpfen geboren","homepage":"http://www.dannythedog-lefilm.com/","overview":"Normales menschliches Verhalten ist ein Fremdwort für Danny, einen jungen Mann mit dem Wissenstand und der sozialen Reife eines kleines Kindes. Von seinem \"Besitzer\" Bart wurde er zur Kampfmaschine gedrillt, muß sich jedoch mit einem Halsband versehen jedoch sonst stets in einem Käfig aufhalten, um für Bart in illegalen Gladiatorenkämpfen mit tödlichem Ausgang anzutreten. Als Bart nach einem schweren Unfall ins Koma verfällt, ist Danny auf einmal auf sich gestellt - und gerät an den blinden Klavierstimmer Sam, der ihn behutsam in die normale Welt einführt und ihm beibringt, was es heißt, ein Mensch zu sein. Nur eines Tages wacht Bart aus seinem Koma wieder auf und will seinen Besitz zurück. Bald steht Danny vor schweren moralischen Entscheidungen..."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Danny the Dog","runtime":103,"tagline":"Incatenato dalla violenza, liberato dalla musica","homepage":"","overview":"Danny è uno schiavo che ha vissuto tutta la sua vita senza mai essere stato educato, con la mentalità di un ragazzino e con un solo ordine in mente: combattere. Il suo padrone lo tratta come un cane e lo costringe ad indossare addirittura un guinzaglio ed a combattere in lotte illegali organizzate nei fight clubs."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Kır Zincirlerini","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Tam 30 yaşına kadar, kendisini annesinden çok küçük yaşta almış Bart adlı adamın ofisinin altındaki küçük bir depoda yaşayan Danny, bir öldürme makinesi olarak eğtilmiştir. Tüm hayatı yaşadığı bu yeraltındaki odadır. Ve ne zaman ihtiyaç duysa Bart'a onun öğrettiği şekilde hizmet etmektedir. Hayatını para satarak kazanan bir tefeci olan Bart, borç verdiği insanlar geri ödemekte zorluk çektiklerinde ya da geciktiklerinde Danny'yi devreye sokar. Onu bir köpek gibi yetiştirmiştir ve her fırsatta silahı olarak kullanmaktadır. Ta ki Bart bir gün kin tutan müşterilerinden biri tarafından tuzağa düşürülene dek. Danny, bu olaydan sonra kendisini sahiplenen sanatçı Sam ve üvey kızı Victoria'nın yanında sevginin ne olduğunu öğrenirken, Bart'ın öldüğüne inanmaktadır. Fakat Bart ölmemiştir; 'köpeğini' geri almak için döndüğünde Danny'nin eski ve yeni hayatı birbirine girer."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Bokmål","iso_639_1":"nb","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian Bokmål"},{"data":{"title":"Danny the Dog","runtime":102,"tagline":"Élévé comme un chien.  Dressé pour tuer.","homepage":"","overview":"Bart a élevé Danny comme un chien, dressé pour tuer. À 30 ans, il ne connaît de la vie que son maître, la pièce dans laquelle il est resté reclus et les combats sanguinaires pour lesquels il est entraîné. Après un règlement de compte, Danny se retrouve seul, perdu. Sam, doux, humain, artiste, et sa belle fille mélomane le recueillent. À force d'amour, de patience et de gentillesse, Sam et Victoria vont défaire le long apprentissage de la violence qu'il a connue."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Danny the Dog - Força Destruidora","runtime":103,"tagline":"Acorrentado pela violência, libertado pela música.","homepage":"","overview":"Essa é a história de Danny (Jet Li), um escravo que sempre viveu numa cave sem qualquer tipo de contacto com o mundo, com a mente e a personalidade de uma pequena criança, tendo aprendido uma única lição: lutar até à morte."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Człowiek Pies","runtime":103,"tagline":"Nie służ żadnemu panu","homepage":"","overview":"Danny (Jet Li), to mężczyzna o umyśle dziecka, którego Bart (Bob Hoskins), jego \"pan i właściciel\", wyszkolił na idealną maszynę do zabijania. Perfekcyjną znajomość wschodnich sztuk walki wykorzystuje w nielegalnych zawodach i przynosi swojemu szefowi spore zyski. Kiedy po wypadku samochodowym Bart trafia do szpitala i zapada w śpiączkę, Danny musi radzić sobie sam. Poznaje niewidomego pianistę (Morgan Freeman), który jako pierwszy traktuje go jak pełnowartościowego człowieka.  [opis dystrybutora dvd]"},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Unleashed","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Danny is een slaaf. Hij heeft zijn hele leven zonder enige vorm van scholing doorgebracht en heeft daarom de ontwikkeling van een kind. Danny wordt door zijn eigenaar Bart als een hond behandeld en moet voor hem vechten in illegale vechtwedstrijden. Als Bart na een auto-ongeluk in een coma belandt, komt Danny bij de blinde pianist Sam terecht die hem in huis neemt en hem de prettige kantjes van het leven laat zien."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Danny the Dog","runtime":125,"tagline":"Entrenado para matar... Pero no para obedecer","homepage":"","overview":"Arrancado de los brazos de su madre por Bart, Danny sólo conoce el mundo que éste le ha mostrado: la habitación en la que vive y los actos de violencia que se ve obligado a cometer cuando las personas a las que Bart presta dinero se retrasan en el pago. Danny es, pues, un hombre adiestrado como un perro para obedecer las órdenes de su amo sin rechistar. Pero, un día, Bart cae en la emboscada que le tiende un deudor vengativo."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Danny The Dog","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Danny känner inte till någon annan värld än den som Bart har visat honom. Bart gav honom kläder, kost och logi. Han tränade upp Danny, på samma sätt som en hund, till att bli en skoningslös mordmaskin - en lydig livvakt och en säker inkomstkälla i brutala gladiatorspel. Nu är Bart försvunnen och Danny ensam i en främmande värld. Hos den åldrande pianisten Sam är han långt från den våldspräglade verklighet som tidigare var hans värld. Han finner sig långsamt tillrätta och förälskar sig även i Sams dotter. Men Bart är inte långt borta och när han plötsligt dyker upp, krockar Dannys två världar på våldsammast tänkbara sätt..."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Utržený ze řetězu","runtime":0,"tagline":"Spoutaný násilím, osvobozený hudbou","homepage":"","overview":"Tohle je příběh o Dannym, otrokovi, který většinu života strávil bez jakéhokoli vzdělání. S osobností a myšlením malého dítěte se naučil pouze jedinou věc: jak bojovat. Jeho vlastník Bart jej donutil nosit obojek. Danny byl vybrán jako bojující stroj, bojující v ilegálních gladiátorských klubech, kde pro Barta vydělává spousty peněz. Po autonehodě, při které Bart upadne do kómatu, se Danny setká se slepým ladičem klavírů, který žije na útěku před lidmi, o kterých ví určité pikantnosti. Používá hudbu, aby naučil Dannyho o světě a pomohl mu stát se člověkem."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"Дани кучето","runtime":102,"tagline":"Не служи на никой господар","homepage":"","overview":"Дани е прекарал целия си живот без нормално човешко възпитание, със съзнанието на дете, което е научило един единствен урок - как да се бие. Третиран като куче от своя собственик (включително и да носи нашийник), Дани е отгледан с цел да участва в нелегални боеве, където той е абсолютния шампион и носи големи печалби на Бърт (собственика си). След автомобилна катастрофа, Бърт изпада в кома, а Дани среща сляп учител по пиано, който му показва света и го научава какво значи да бъдеш човек..."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"Дэнни Цепной пёс","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Дэнни — человек. Он — не собака и вообще не зверь. Но он ходит в ошейнике, спит в ошейнике, ест в ошейнике, почти круглые сутки он проводит в ошейнике. Потому что таким его воспитал Барт, гангстер из Глазго, собиратель долгов, не брезгующий никакими методами при достижении поставленной цели. Когда ему не отдают долг, у него быстро лопается терпение, и тогда Барт снимает с Дэнни ошейник. И Дэнни превращается в собаку, в злобного бультерьера, в адскую смесь жестокого зверя и неудержимого боевого киборга.  Нет на свете соперника, равного Дэнни в поединке. Дэнни не знает иной жизни, кроме полусонного существования в ошейнике или смертельной битвы без ошейника. Однажды волею судьбы он оказывается в доме, где живут старый слепой пианист Сэм и его приемная дочь Виктория. Дэнни узнает, что есть иная жизнь, в которой есть чувства, краски, звуки…"},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"狼犬丹尼","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"高利贷商人巴特（Bob Hoskins 饰）在丹尼（李连杰 饰）四岁时将他收留，从此用训练猛兽的方式让丹尼成为自己忠实的“狼犬”。巴特日常的工作是带领自己的手下与丹尼四处收账，如有任何人胆敢暴力反抗，巴特就放开丹尼颈上的项圈——那是进攻的信号，让后者用蛮横凶残的招式击溃对方。每次任务结束，丹尼都被送回阴暗的地下铁笼。  某次打斗中，丹尼偶遇盲调音师山姆（Morgan Freeman 饰），并为钢琴所深深吸引以致忘记了巴特的任务。盛怒的巴特将丹尼送上以死亡为终结的地下拳场，赚取了更多的利润，在离开拳场的路上巴特一伙遭仇家埋伏，丹尼幸免于难，被山姆一家收留。在山姆家里丹尼体味到缺失的亲情，逐渐找回了自身的人性一面，并开始学习弹奏钢琴。巴特等人经过治疗后痊愈，再次将丹尼拉回到拳场，然而丹尼已不再愿意杀人，无意中又发现了当年自己母亲遇害的真相，丹尼与巴特一伙的决战在所难免……"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"A nyakörv","runtime":103,"tagline":"Törj ki a rabságból!","homepage":"","overview":"Bart 4 éves korában elrabolta Dannyt, azóta úgy bánik vele, mint egy állattal. Danny képes az első parancsszóra rátámadni bárkire a legcsekélyebb esélyt sem adva ellenfelének. Egy nap Danny véletlenül találkozik Sammel, a vak zongorahangolóval. Sam és mostohalánya Victoria megismertetik vele az emberi természetnek azt az oldalát, ami számára eddig ismeretlen volt. Így Danny életről alkotott képe lassan megváltozik. Megpróbál önmaga lenni és múltjának titkait felderíteni, immár Barttal és bandájával szembeszállva."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Danny the Dog","runtime":98,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Danny har aldrig kendt andre verdener end den, Bart viste ham. Bart gav ham tøj, kost og logi. Og som en hund trænede han Danny op som en nådesløs dræbermaskine – en lydig bodyguard og sikker indtjeningskilde ved brutale gladiatorkampe. Nu er Bart væk og Danny alene i en verden, han ikke kender. Hos den aldrende pianist, Sam, er han langt fra den voldsverden, han kom fra. Langsomt falder han til og forelsker sig i Sams datter. Men Bart er ikke langt væk, og da han pludselig dukker op, kolliderer Dannys to verdener på voldsomste vis…"},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":103,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ο Ντάνι Λι, ένας σκλάβος με μυαλό παιδιού, έχει μεγαλώσει στα χέρια του σκληρού Μπαρτ, που τον έχει εκπαιδεύσει κυριολεκτικά σαν σκύλο. Ο αφέντης του, του φορά κολάρο και τον χρησιμοποιεί σε παράνομους αγώνες πυγμαχίας, όπου ο Ντάνι μεταμορφώνεται σε φονική μηχανή. Όταν όμως ο Ντάνι το σκάσει κι ένας τυφλός πιανίστας του προσφέρει καταφύγιο, θα ανακαλύψει στους ήχους της μουσικής το μεγαλειώδες δώρο της ανθρωπιάς...  Ο πρωταθλητής των πολεμικών τεχνών ΤΖΕΤ ΛΙ συναντά τους βραβευμένους με Όσκαρ ΜΟΡΓΚΑΝ ΦΡΙΜΑΝ και με Χρυσή Σφαίρα ΜΠΟΜΠ ΧΟΣΚΙΝΣ σε μια σκοτεινή περιπέτεια με καταιγιστική δράση! Με σενάριο του ΛΙΚ ΜΠΕΣΟΝ και σκηνοθεσία του δημιουργού των σούπερ-επιτυχιών \"The Transporter 1 &amp; 2\" ΛΟΥΙ ΛΕΤΕΡΙΕ, η ταινία είναι πλημμυρισμένη με σκηνές ασταμάτητης δράσης και βίας ενώ το υποβλητικό soundtrack υπογράφουν οι MASSIVE ATTACK."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"ללא מחסום","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"דני הוא איש צעיר אשר מתנהג כמו כלב, כשהאדון שלו מוריד לו את הרצועה מהצוואר הוא מכסח את כל מי שבא בדרכו. האדון שלו משתמש בדני כהימור בטוח בקרבות נגד אחרים. יום אחד קוראת תאונה, ודני רואה אפשרות לברוח והוא לוקח אותה, הוא מגיע לאיש עיוור (שמקצועו מכוון פסנתרים) אשר הכירו לפני כן. האיש העיוור ובתו מלמדים את דני את כל מה שהוא לא הספיק ללמוד ולהבין במשך החיים שלו."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Cão de Briga","runtime":0,"tagline":"Soltá-lo pode ser fatal.","homepage":"","overview":"Desde que Bart tirou Danny da rua, com a idade de 4 anos, sempre o tratou como um cão, treinando-o literalmente para o ataque. Danny é hoje sua grande arma, capaz de se atirar sobre qualquer um com uma simples ordem. Mas as coisas mudam quando ele conhece Sam, um cego que ganha a vida como afinador de pianos. Sam faz Danny descobrir um lado humano que até então lhe era desconhecido."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"鬥犬","runtime":103,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"盧貝松親自編劇監製，功夫皇帝李連杰和摩根費里曼主演。李連杰在片中再度展現拳腳功夫的長才。  由李連杰所飾演的丹尼自小就被鮑勃霍斯金當成狼犬般飼養，在脖子戴上項圈，被訓練成致命的殺人武器，也未曾受過正常教育，而他的心智年齡始終如孩童般天真，不知外在的世界為何，在一次車禍意外下，丹尼認識了由摩根費里曼所飾演的瞎眼鋼琴調音師，費里曼用音樂教導他新的人生意義，耳濡目染下，丹尼有了全然不同的體驗，新的人生才正要開始，而更大的危險正一步步的靠近他，該如何擺脫命運的糾纏，就看上天巧妙的安排了！..."},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Dresat pentru a ucide","runtime":103,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Din momentul în care Bart l-a smuls pe Danny de lângă mama lui, l-a tratat întotdeauna ca pe un câine, dresându-l, practic, pentru atac. Danny reprezintă astăzi arma lui absolută, gata să se arunce asupra oricui, fară a-i lasă nici cea mai mica șansă de scăpare. Rupt de lume, Danny nu are de ales, trebuind să accepte existența sa de animal, până când, îl întâlnește pe Sam, un orb care îi va schimba întregul mod de a percepe viața."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"더 독","runtime":100,"tagline":"내가 곧 규칙이다. 오직 나의 명령에 복종만 있을 뿐!!!","homepage":"","overview":"싸워라! 죽여라! 이겨라!  어두운 지하 창고.  흔들리는 눈빛, 구부정한 어깨, 암울한 표정, 주춤거리는 발걸음의 한 남자가 걸어오고 있다.  그의 목엔 금속의 차가운 족쇄가 채어져 있고 그의 옆엔 냉소적인 웃음을 띤 흰 양복을  입은 남자가 서있다. 하얀 양복을 입은 남자가 속삭이는 한마디! “KILL HIM”  그리고 그가 하고있는 목의 족쇄를 풀어준다. 순간 초점 없던 그의 눈은 날카롭게 빛나고,  혀를 내두를 만큼 빠른 몸놀림과 힘 앞에 상대편 남자들은 하나 둘 쓰러져 간다.  인간이 아닌 투견으로 사육되어진 남자… DANNY  그에겐 기억도, 감정도, 사고도 허락치 않는다!  그의 이름은 대니(이연걸). 그는 하얀 양복을 입은 남자, 바트(밥호스킨스)에 의해 길러졌다.  그가 바트에게 배운 것이라고는 명령에 복종하며 시키는 대로 싸우고 죽이는 일 뿐.  차가운 쇠창살 안에 개처럼 키워진 대니에게는 지난 날의 기억도, 인간의 감정도, 사고도  없다. 강아지에게 달려드는 성난 투견처럼 먹이를 향해 몸을 날리는 것만이 오직 그의  삶이다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Денні - пес","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Дені - людина, навчена як пес і підготовлена своїм господарем для найстрашніших злочинів. У перестрілці Дені-пес втрачає свого господаря і випадково потрапляє до сім'ї, де панує любов і спокій. Він дізнається, що потрібно цінувати доброту, ласку і турботу. Але господар вижив і жадає повернути свого ланцюгового пса. Минуле і сьогодення стикаються в смертельній сутичці, що несе страшні наслідки для всіх..."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"Danny: La Bestia (Unleashed)","runtime":0,"tagline":"Entrenado para matar... Pero no para obedecer","homepage":"","overview":"Arrancado de los brazos de su madre por Bart, Danny sólo conoce el mundo que éste le ha mostrado: la habitación en la que vive y los actos de violencia que se ve obligado a cometer cuando las personas a las que Bart presta dinero se retrasan en el pago. Danny es, pues, un hombre adiestrado como un perro para obedecer las órdenes de su amo sin rechistar. Pero, un día, Bart cae en la emboscada que le tiende un deudor vengativo."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Danny The Dog","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Danny har aldri kjent andre verdener enn den som Bart viste ham. Han fikk klær, kost og losji av Bart. Som en hund trente han opp Danny som en nådesløs drapsmaskin - en lydig bodyguard og sikker inntekstskilde ved brutale gladiatorkamper. Nå er Bart borte og Danny er alene i en verden han ikke kjenner. Hos den aldrende pianisten, Sam, er han langt borte fra den voldelige verden han kom fra. Langsomt finner han seg til rette og forelsker seg i Sams datter. Men Bart er ikke langt borte, og da han plutselig dukker opp, kolliderer Dannys to verdener på verste måte…"},"name":"Norsk","iso_639_1":"no","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian"},{"data":{"title":"Šuo Denis","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Denis yra profesionalus kovotojas, dirbantis mafijos bosui Bartui, kuris su Deniu elgiasi kaip su šunimi. Denis turi net apykaklę, kurią nuėmus jis pradeda elgtis kaip žvėris, puldinėdamas ir žalodamas žmones pagal šeimininko Barto įsakymą.  Nuo pat mažumės Denis buvo augintas kaip kovinė mašina, padedanti Bartui prievartauti ir reketuoti žmones, o taip pat uždirbti galybes pinigų pogrindiniuose kovų klubuose. Įvykus nelaimingam atsitikimui, kurio metu Denį ištinka koma, jis patenka į gerų žmonių rankas."},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"},{"data":{"title":"คนหมาเดือด","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"บาร์ท (บ็อบ ฮอสกิ้นส์) เลี้ยงดูสั่งสอน แดนนี่ (เจ็ท ลี) เยี่ยงสุนัขในอาณัติ แดนนี่ได้รับการฝึกฝนศิลปะการต่อสู้ และขัดเกลาฝีมือจนได้เป็นอาวุธเด็ดของเจ้านาย เมื่อตกอยู่ภายใต้อำนาจเช่นนี้ แดนนี่รับรู้เพียงว่าต้องเชื่อฟัง และทำตามคำสั่งของบาร์ท และไม่เคยได้รับอิสรภาพและมีชีวิตอยู่อย่างเสรี"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"აწყვეტილი","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"დენის ბავშვობიდან მონასავით ექცევიან და წვრთნიან როგორც ძაღლს, მხოლოდ ერთი მიზეზით - რომ მისგან სიკვდილის მანქანა შექმნან, გლადიატორული ბრძოლებისთვის. საბოლოოდ 21 წლის ასაკში, დენი ყველაფერში ბავშვია, გარდა ჩხუბებისა. ერთი ინციდენტის შედეგად, ის განთავისუფლდება და შეხვდება კეთილ, ბრმა პიანინოების ამწყობს, რომელიც თვალებს აუხელს ამ ცხოვრებაზე."},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"},{"data":{"title":"ダニー・ザ・ドッグ","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"5歳の時に誘拐され、悪徳高利貸しによって“闘犬”になるべく育てられた男ダニー。常に首輪をはめられ、脅迫要員として借金の取り立てと闘いに明け暮れていたが、盲目のピアノ調律師との出会いを通して、次第に人間性を取り戻していく……。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"Odtrhnutý z reťaze","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Toto je príbeh o Dannym, otrokovi, ktorý väčšinu života strávil bez akéhokoľvek vzdelania. S osobnosťou a myslením malého dieťaťa sa naučil iba jedinú vec, ako bojovať. Jeho vlastník Bart ho donútil nosiť obojok. Danny bol vybraný ako vražedný stroj, bojujúci v ilegálnych gladiátorských kluboch, kde pre Barta zarába množstvo peňazí. Po autonehode, z ktorej miesta ušiel pred Bartom, sa Danny stretne so slepým ladičom klavírov a jeho nevlastnou dcérou. Používajú hudbu, aby naučili Dannyho o svete a pomohli mu stať sa človekom."},"name":"Slovenčina","iso_639_1":"sk","iso_3166_1":"SK","english_name":"Slovak"},{"data":{"title":"Danny the Dog","runtime":103,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Danny ei tiedä maailmasta muuta kuin sen vähän, jonka Bart on sallinut hänen nähdä. Bart antaa Dannylle ruokaa, vaatteet ja katon pään päälle ja koiran pannan kaulaan. Omistajan oikeudella Bart kouluttaa Dannya kuin koiraa, jotta julmasti alistettu mies voi toimia Bartin henkivartijana ja voittaa tälle omaisuuksia verisissä gladiaattoritaisteluissa. Mutta nyt Bart on poissa ja Danny jää yksin. Koulutettu tappokone ei tunne ketään muita ihmisiä, eikä osaa kommunikoida lainkaan. Sitten Danny tapaa sokean Samin, joka yrittää opettaa Dannya olemaan ihmisiksi. Taistelulajien armoitettu mestari on Danny orvoksi jäänyt poika, jota lapsesta saakka on kasvatettu kuin koiraa tavoitteena muokata pojasta taisteluareenoiden rahasampo. Pojasta kasvaa verenhimoinen vahtikoira, joka joutuu eksyksiin kun vartioitava katoaa viereltä. Sam tarjoaa Dannylle mahdollisuutta uuteen elämään. Mutta samalla Sam saattaa itsensä ja perheensä ennen kokemattomaan vaaraan."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"Danny The Dog","runtime":0,"tagline":"Entrenat per matar... Però no per obeir","homepage":"","overview":"Arrancat dels braços de la seva mare per Bart, Danny només coneix el món que aquest li ha mostrat: l'habitació on viu i els actes de violència que es veu obligat a cometre quan les persones a qui Bart presta diners s'endarrereixen a el pagament. Danny és, doncs, un home ensinistrat com un gos per obeir les ordres del seu amo sense dir ni piu. Però, un dia, Bart cau a l'emboscada que li tendeix un deutor venjatiu."},"name":"Català","iso_639_1":"ca","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Catalan"},{"data":{"title":"Mắt Xích Tử Thần","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Enchaîné","runtime":103,"tagline":"Ne servez aucun maître","homepage":"","overview":"Forcé par un gangster à participer à des combats mortels, un as des arts martiaux s'enfuit et se lie d'amitié avec un aveugle et une jeune musicienne."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"鬥犬","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"盧貝松親自編劇監製，功夫皇帝李聯傑和摩根費裏曼主演。李聯傑在片中再度展現拳腳功夫的長才。\r 由李聯傑所飾演的丹尼自小就被鮑勃霍斯金當成狼犬般飼養，在脖子戴上項圈，被訓練成致命的殺人武器，也未曾受過正常教育，而他的心智年齡始終如孩童般天真，不知外在的世界為何，在一次車禍意外下，丹尼認識了由摩根費裏曼所飾演的瞎眼鋼琴調音師，費裏曼用音樂教導他新的人生意義，耳濡目染下，丹尼有了全然不同的體驗，新的人生才正要開始，而更大的危險正一步步的靠近他，該如何擺脱命運的糾纏，就看上天巧妙的安排了！. . ."},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":2140,"adult":false,"title":"Kiss of the Dragon","video":false,"overview":"Liu Jian, an elite Chinese police officer, comes to Paris to arrest a Chinese drug lord. When Jian is betrayed by a French officer and framed for murder, he must go into hiding and find new allies.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.4524,"vote_count":1302,"poster_path":"/1ubtSyagwfNF9Bn9s2CKITRtx1d.jpg","release_date":"2001-07-06","vote_average":6.891,"backdrop_path":"/9S0BHQuZAyNMG0GpHAMSIbF38au.jpg","original_title":"Kiss of the Dragon","original_language":"en"},{"id":10623,"adult":false,"title":"Cradle 2 the Grave","video":false,"overview":"Gang leader Tony pulls off a major diamond heist with his crew, but cop-turned-criminal Ling knows who has the loot and responds by kidnapping Tony's daughter and holding her for ransom. Unfortunately, Tony's lost the diamonds as well. As he frantically searches for his daughter and the jewels, Tony pairs with a high-kicking government agent who once worked with Ling and seeks revenge on him.","genre_ids":[28,80,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.4629,"vote_count":989,"poster_path":"/8iXpVITXenqPG8gQ0lCFpUMtZIx.jpg","release_date":"2003-02-28","vote_average":6.11,"backdrop_path":"/jp5Gir5wCxpt9dzIZLauCFy1X95.jpg","original_title":"Cradle 2 the Grave","original_language":"en"},{"id":2085,"adult":false,"title":"Romeo Must Die","video":false,"overview":"Two warring gang families (one African-American, the other Chinese) maneuver for bragging rights to the Oakland, California, docks. Hang Sing and Trish O'Day uncover a trail of deceit that leaves most of the warring factions dead … or worse!","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.5782,"vote_count":1305,"poster_path":"/zKrnaTWW63y4Q1XLrdZQyQmcRWd.jpg","release_date":"2000-03-22","vote_average":6.264,"backdrop_path":"/hq5bbmRj65ald90E3PlWyzOtl7D.jpg","original_title":"Romeo Must Die","original_language":"en"},{"id":7549,"adult":false,"title":"Fearless","video":false,"overview":"After going through a series of tragic events in his life, martial arts master Huo Yuanjia returns to Tianjin and must fight four international soldiers, in order to safeguard his nation's pride.","genre_ids":[18,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.4189,"vote_count":1371,"poster_path":"/yKJ7rjIwOa8XvACELo9eV8IvMPb.jpg","release_date":"2006-01-26","vote_average":7.509,"backdrop_path":"/6epfs9UMFbYuj4UfjHq5EDic8V9.jpg","original_title":"霍元甲","original_language":"zh"},{"id":1441,"adult":false,"title":"The Contract","video":false,"overview":"Attempting to recover from a recent family trauma by escaping into the woods for a peaceful hiking trip, an ex-lawman and his young son stumble across a dangerous contract killer.","genre_ids":[18,28,53,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.6255,"vote_count":538,"poster_path":"/sU2yzV3T1LetBdQPAeBRDb4YwLo.jpg","release_date":"2006-04-05","vote_average":5.732,"backdrop_path":"/btd9VPSfnVh0pHZqbiUJLsOkBDf.jpg","original_title":"The Contract","original_language":"en"},{"id":1729,"adult":false,"title":"The Forbidden Kingdom","video":false,"overview":"An American teenager who is obsessed with Hong Kong cinema and kung-fu classics makes an extraordinary discovery in a Chinatown pawnshop: the legendary stick weapon of the Chinese sage and warrior, the Monkey King. With the lost relic in hand, the teenager unexpectedly finds himself travelling back to ancient China to join a crew of warriors from martial arts lore on a dangerous quest to free the imprisoned Monkey King.","genre_ids":[28,12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.493,"vote_count":1865,"poster_path":"/z8chF1Z7hyuSVqLYTgElkQZh2VB.jpg","release_date":"2008-04-17","vote_average":6.623,"backdrop_path":"/9a59H9qoAzMcj1NWurMgvg9iLaT.jpg","original_title":"The Forbidden Kingdom","original_language":"en"},{"id":13637,"adult":false,"title":"Sukiyaki Western Django","video":false,"overview":"A nameless gunfighter arrives in a town ripped apart by rival gangs and, though courted by both to join, chooses his own path.","genre_ids":[12,28,35,37,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9378,"vote_count":355,"poster_path":"/6GLjfl1Atsawd5Aq83Qc4fQ9W1T.jpg","release_date":"2007-09-15","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":"/qjii