backdrop_path":"/yspDVgkogQFaW23a58ISEMRW4iq.jpg","original_title":"Who Is Cletis Tout?","original_language":"en"},{"id":496874,"adult":false,"title":"My Dead Ones","video":false,"overview":"Behind the looks of a shy film student, Davi hides an obscure past that is about to be revealed.","genre_ids":[80,18,27],"popularity":0.1857,"vote_count":39,"poster_path":"/u6ITIkFs6eZsMp3KtW5jVjGYlSC.jpg","release_date":"2018-11-22","vote_average":5.3,"backdrop_path":"/4YkeKPaEbnCF2FmXALrzPt9hGDn.jpg","original_title":"O Segredo de Davi","original_language":"pt"},{"id":298667,"adult":false,"title":"Vengeance is Mine","video":true,"overview":"Following the attack on his precinct, Kane buries his friends and sets his sights on avenging their deaths. He assembles a new team and follows the trail across the border to Vancouver.","genre_ids":[18,28,80],"popularity":0.4584,"vote_count":15,"poster_path":"/yVYuz8qkqvpIBHbXDWkt4I6Zt49.jpg","release_date":"2012-06-25","vote_average":5.9,"backdrop_path":"/7FhgMTUlAE4v91NJq3IJaZCrHv0.jpg","original_title":"Vengeance is Mine","original_language":"en"},{"id":298849,"adult":false,"title":"In the Hero","video":false,"overview":"Veteran suit actor Wataru Honjo, a 48-year-old Bruce Lee fan who has spent 25 years in the business, clashes with rookie Ryo Ichinose until fate brings them together—leading Wataru to a once-in-a-lifetime chance to take on a dangerous Hollywood action role.","genre_ids":[28,35],"popularity":0.4489,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/e5BEbcAEBCmrqRhmr6OWp9UkBaE.jpg","release_date":"2014-09-06","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/bCNxPLjswHLkuvCHdQh97oloOff.jpg","original_title":"イン・ザ・ヒーロー","original_language":"ja"},{"id":33537,"adult":false,"title":"Legend of the Wolf","video":false,"overview":"Wolf is a war veteran who recounts the tale of his legendary youth to a young upstart killer. Flashback to a post-World War 2 time when the young Wolf is wandering the Chinese countryside in search of his missing memories. He only knows to meet someone at an abandoned temple. He ends up hooking up with a local villager, who intends to guide the Wolf to his destination. On the way, they find Wai-Yee, who’s been waiting for Wolf for quite some time. However, Wolf still can’t remember anything, until the bad guys come to find him, and they bear the terrible secret of the Wolf's past.","genre_ids":[28],"popularity":0.7414,"vote_count":33,"poster_path":"/cq2qsC19lPVM8OhPiESucvrJJ5e.jpg","release_date":"1997-06-14","vote_average":5.3,"backdrop_path":"/fNEOkaaIALWwqOru4mbjNVkOP3w.jpg","original_title":"戰狼傳說","original_language":"cn"},{"id":33542,"adult":false,"title":"Rumble in the Bronx","video":false,"overview":"Keong comes from Hong Kong to visit New York for his uncle's wedding. His uncle runs a market in the Bronx and Keong offers to help out while Uncle is on his honeymoon. During his stay in the Bronx, Keong befriends a neighbor kid and beats up some neighborhood thugs who cause problems at the market. One of those petty thugs in the local gang stumbles into a criminal situation way over his head.","genre_ids":[80,28,35,53],"popularity":3.3449,"vote_count":1126,"poster_path":"/1nAfchiXHQB3iyhK8fCJJEnNs5A.jpg","release_date":"1995-01-21","vote_average":6.821,"backdrop_path":"/5ftRls3IbR1kXnasqJEJL63LVsc.jpg","original_title":"紅番區","original_language":"cn"},{"id":299041,"adult":false,"title":"The Himalayan","video":false,"overview":"The Tseng family is one of the most noble and respected clans in a small village in Tibet. The patriarch of the Tseng family wants to marry off his daughter Ching Lan into the Kao clan. However, the cunning and deceitful eldest brother Kao Chu only wants his younger sibling Kao I-Fan to marry Lan so he can gain access to the Tseng family's considerable wealth and power.","genre_ids":[18,28],"popularity":0.6434,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/btZeEK4KHNPrPL5EX2OqDHKR17f.jpg","release_date":"1976-02-20","vote_average":3.5,"backdrop_path":"/kHBl3AXO75Wawc8rC94kkxFGoHZ.jpg","original_title":"密宗聖手","original_language":"zh"},{"id":36209,"adult":false,"title":"Zombie vs. Ninja","video":false,"overview":"Ethan, a young man, is beaten while his father is killed by a group of thieves. With the help of an undertaker, Ethan trains in kung fu by fighting the dead. Meanwhile, an American Ninja, Dragon, must fend off against the thieves and their ninja henchmen. It is soon that Dragon and Ethan team up to defeat the thieves and the ninjas.  Hong Kong cut and paste edit of the 1983 Korean Horror Martial Arts Film \"소화성 장의사\" (The Undertaker in Sohwa Province) with new ninja scenes.","genre_ids":[27,28,35],"popularity":0.294,"vote_count":14,"poster_path":"/o819Hj9P1FpjVKoTHMVqoKueGcG.jpg","release_date":"1987-01-01","vote_average":3.9,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"魔幻狂迷","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt0342258","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q470507","instagram_id":null,"metacritic_id":"movie/unleashed","mydramalist_id":"62361","rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/danny_the_dog"},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":148310,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"AU","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2005-08-18T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"MA 15+"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2005-11-04T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"14"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"CH","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2005-02-02T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"16"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2005-09-01T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","release_dates":[